Virtualization:
Allows to create multiple simulated enviroments or dedicated resources from a singgle, physical hardware system
Hypervisor/host of virtual system. Can be installed as app or system.
Virtual machine / Guest. Functions as single data file. VM does not interact directly with the host machine. Physical hardware is assigned to VMs.

